'''Antibiotice Iaşi''' is a [[public company|public]] pharmaceutical company which is the third largest [[Medication|drug]] producing company in [[Romania]] and a large [[nystatin]] producer. It is 53.02%-owned by the Romanian [[Ministry of Health (Romania)|Ministry of Health]].<ref>[http://www.wall-street.ro/articol/Companii/56169/Privatizari-839-mil-lei-in-primele-9-luni.html Privatizari 839 mil. lei in primele 9 luni] {{Ro icon}}</ref> Its research center and production facilities are based in [[Valea Lupului]], a commune near [[Iaşi]].

